"Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-8j3jp95","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\phi _i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-rjqkg0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-rjqkg0k","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\phi _o"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-syl81yt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-syl81yt","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f(\\theta_i, \\theta_o, \\phi)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-ge2dwcg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-ge2dwcg","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"a65ae4967cfab6e5a8fff7ba3e9824ed_1440w"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/net-img-a65ae4967cfab6e5a8fff7ba3e9824ed_1440w-20240609102013-2ld4ug7.webp"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-omygtpl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-omygtpl","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至于"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"为什么BRDF要定义成辐射率和辐照度的比值，而不是直接定义为辐射率和辐射率比值"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，有两种解释。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-yxxst6z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-yxxst6z","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第一种解释"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以参看"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://www.zhihu.com/question/28476602/answer/41003204","TextMarkTextContent":"brdf为什么要定义为一个单位是sr-1的量？"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-yohxgh5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-yohxgh5","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们结合下面辐照度（A）和辐射率（B）测量仪的示意图来看看。辐照度测量仪（A）接受平面上半球的所有光线，可以测量一个较小面积来自于四面八方的所有光通量，光通量"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Phi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除以传感器面积"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"A"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就可以得到辐照度"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"E"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。辐射度测量仪（B）则有一个长筒控制光线只能从一个很小的立体角进入测量仪，光通量"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Phi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"除以传感器面积"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"A"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和立体角"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\omega"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就可以得到辐射率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-07yfcil","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-07yfcil","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"测平面上一点在某一个方向的出射辐射率很简单，只需要用仪器（B）从该方向对准该点就可以了。而测平面一点入射的辐射率则没有那么简单，必须保证光源正好覆盖测量仪开口立体角，大了该点会接受到比测量值更多的光照，导致测量值比实际值小，小了则与仪器的设计立体角不一致，可在实际中是基本做不到光源大小正好覆盖测量仪开口立体角的。而测表面的辐照度则简单得多，只要保证光源很小，而且没有来自其他方向的光干扰，这时候测到的辐照度就是平面上来自光源方向的微分辐照度"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"dE"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-jy7wfbt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-jy7wfbt","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"77aa9a3b3302d240ed5093bbf4d46625_1440w"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/net-img-77aa9a3b3302d240ed5093bbf4d46625_1440w-20240609102014-34ob9xe.webp"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-qd9i2xy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-qd9i2xy","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em em em","TextMarkTextContent":"第二种"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"解释"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"**从数学的角度出发，对于现实世界中的非光学平面，一束光线射到表面上后，被表面反射到各个方向，其中一个出射方向的光通量只是整个反射光通量极小的一部分，当出射方向立体角趋于0时，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\lim_{\\omega _{o}   \\rightarrow 0}{\\frac{dL_{o} }{Li} } = 0"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，所以在实际计算中使用辐射率和辐射率比值是没有意义的。而如果分母改成表面上接收到的来自光源方向的微分辐照度，我们知道"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"dE = L_i(l) d\\omega _{i} cos \\theta _{i}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，由于给入射辐射率乘了一个趋于零的微分立体角，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"dE"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的值会小很多，比值"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\frac{dL_o}{dE}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是有意义的，而不是0。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-jd744kw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-jd744kw","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们来看看"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"怎么用BRDF来计算表面辐射率"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-24221m4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-24221m4","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们考虑来自方向"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"l"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的入射光辐射率"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_i(l)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，由辐射率和辐照度的定义："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-jrwjqjo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-jrwjqjo","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_i(l) = \\frac{d \\Phi }{d\\omega_i d A^{\\bot } }  =  \\frac{d \\Phi }{d\\omega_i dA cos \\theta_i } = \\frac{dE(l) }{d\\omega_i cos \\theta_i }"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n则照射到表面来自于方向"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"l"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的入射光贡献的微分辐照度："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-ao8tob6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-ao8tob6","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"dE(l) = L_i(l) d\\omega_i cos \\theta_i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表面反射到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"v"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方向的由来自于方向"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"l"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的入射光贡献的微分辐射率："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-vj7u564","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-vj7u564","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"dL_o(v) = f(l, v) \\otimes  dE(l) = f(l, v) \\otimes L_i(l) d\\omega_i cos \\theta_i"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-jffzrhs","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-jffzrhs","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20240609101959-txi448x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-txi448x","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"符号"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\otimes"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"表示按向量的分量相乘，因为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"和"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"都包含RGB三个分量。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-247et6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-247et6t","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"要计算表面反射到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"v"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方向的来自上半球所有方向入射光线贡献的辐射率，可以将上式对半球所有方向的光线积分："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-x02pa5k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-x02pa5k","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_o(v) = \\int_{\\Omega }^{} f(l, v) \\otimes L_i(l) cos \\theta_i d\\omega_i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n上式称为"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"反射方程（Reflectance Equation）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，用来计算表面反射辐射率。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-pdlwd57","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-pdlwd57","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"对于点光源、方向光等理想化的精准光源（Punctual Light）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，计算过程可以大大简化。我们考察单个精准光源照射表面，此时表面上的一点只会被来自一个方向的一条光线照射到（而面积光源照射表面时，表面上一点会被来自多个方向的多条光线照射到），则辐射率："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-iz0zvfo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-iz0zvfo","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_o(v) = f(l, v) \\otimes E_L cos \\theta_i"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n对于多个精准光源，只需简单累加就可以了："}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-pdcyp9t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-pdcyp9t","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"L_o(v) = \\sum_{k = 1}^{n}{f(l_k, v) \\otimes E_{L_k} cos \\theta_{i_k}}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这里使用光源的辐照度，对于阳光等全局方向光，可以认为整个场景的辐照度是一个常数，对于点光源，辐照度随距离的平方衰减，用公式"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"E_{L} = \\frac{\\Phi }{4\\pi r^2}"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"就可以求出到达表面的辐照度，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"\\Phi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是光源的功率，比如100瓦的灯泡，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"r"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"是表面离光源的距离。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-gxs97tp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-gxs97tp","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"回头看看反射方程，是对表面上半球所有方向的入射光线积分，这里面包含了来自精准光源的光线，也包括周围环境反射的光线。处理来自周围环境的光线可以大幅提高光照的真实程度，在实时图形学中，这部分光照可以用"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"基于图像的光照（Image Based Lighting）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来模拟。我们将在下篇文章讨论基于图像的光照。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-562t1r8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-562t1r8","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面给出了BRDF的定义和使用BRDF计算表面反射辐射率的公式。但这个定义实际上是无法直接用于计算表面反射辐射率的，我们还要建立一个能模拟真实光照的模型，使得输入入射方向和出射方向，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"inline-math","TextMarkInlineMathContent":"f(l, v)"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能输出表面反射微分辐射率和入射微分辐照度的比率。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-fvfkcdu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-fvfkcdu","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1967年Torrance-Sparrow在Theory for Off-Specular Reflection From Roughened Surfaces中使用辐射度学和微表面理论建立了模拟真实光照的BRDF模型，1981年Cook-Torrance在A Reflectance Model for Computer Graphics中把这个模型引入到计算机图形学领域，现在这个模型已经成为基于物理着色的标准，被称为Cook-Torrance模型。下面我们来看看微表面理论和Cook-Torrance模型的推导过程。"}]},{"ID":"20240609101959-jdzqo2d","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240609101959-jdzqo2d","updated":"20240609101959"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"微表面理论"}]},{"ID":"2024